[SkillPath "competitive_bidding/takeout_doubles"]
[Student "S"]
{The bidding has been as shown.   

Don't even think about bidding 1NT. You are way way too weak for that. Don't even think about passing for penalties. Your \D are nowhere near good enough. Partner is forcing you to bid a suit, so you bid your best non-\D suit, \Hs. Partner now jumps to 2\S.  

You say pass. Despite partner showing you a big hand you just can't help him. }

[Event ""]
[Site ""]
[Date ""]
[Board "3"]
[Dealer "N"]
